==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stridulate
<hw>Strid"u*late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Stridulous</er>.]</ety> <def>To make a shrill, creaking noise</def>;
specifically <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <def>to make a shrill or musical sound,
such as is made by the males of many insects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stridulation</ent>⟦br⟧
